title: Errant Rocket Fired By Terrorist Group
content: US President Joe Biden said Tuesday that an 'errant rocket' fired by a 'terrorist group' caused a devastating explosion at a Gaza hospital that left hundreds dead. Listen to the latest songs, only on JioSaavn.com. Based on the information we've seen to date, it appears as a result of an errant rocket fired by a terrorist group in Gaza, Joe Biden told reporters at the end of a short trip to show solidarity with Israel after the October 7 Hamas attacks.
